酢昆布ですよ

90
00:08:09,929 --> 00:08:11,929
SUKONBU?

91
00:08:12,719 --> 00:08:15,849
SUKONBU SUKONBU SUKONBU

92
00:08:15,849 --> 00:08:17,979
SUKONBU SU...

